The '''Quagmire Firepit''' is a structure found in the game during the Gorge event. Unlike normal [[Fire Pit/DST|Fire Pit]], it cannot be used to cook food directly. Instead, [[Cooking stations]] need to be installed on it in order to cook [[The Gorge Recipes|dishes]] exclusive to the event. It needs fuel such as logs to function.
